name: Ishat
description:
I use a variety of neural networks to explore the potential of what state-of-the-art machines can think and create. 

Each piece of this Sultana Collection contains the essence of a magical Djinn (on the left) inhabiting a middle-eastern city (center), and the effect of his influence on the royal Sultana (right). Each piece is named by an artificial intelligence trained in generating female Arabic names. 
Artist: @PhenoTrope
Medium: PNG
Dimensions: 7786 x 5129
Creation Date: 10/9/2021
